    "content": "<p>Title : BA (Hons) Public Relations and Marketing Communications</p>\n<p><a rel=\"noopener\" href=\"https://scqf.org.uk/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Scottish Credit and Qualifications Framework\">SCQF Level</a> : 10</p>\n<p>Mode of delivery and duration : Four year full-time programme (classroom-based) with option to travel to QMU to undertake the final year of study in Edinburgh</p>\n<p>Language of delivery : English</p>"
